4WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11708] added new syntax for redirecting stderr and stdout+stderr with a pipe
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11766] fixed file completions for glob patterns
fdncred bumped some versions (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11804] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11793] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11715] 3
), 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11797] made it easier to convert 
``int``
s, to 
``filesize``
s
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11781] made 
``ansi strip``
 work for more data types
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11771] made the 
``char``
 command 
``const``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11724] allowed strings with thousands separators to be converted to filesize or ints
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11792] upgraded the hustcer/setup-nu GitHub action
nibon7 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11788] upgraded miette from 5.10.0 to 7.0.0
kubouch bumped some versions (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11787] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11782] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11730] 3
), 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11719] improved 
``def``
 body parsing
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11718] fixed a panic in 
``rotate``
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11786] added a serde feature for 
``byte-unit``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11772] fixed up a 
``LazyRecord``
 error message
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11726] refactored some Record code
abusch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11748] allowed specifying a cellpath in 
``input list``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11742] upgraded to ratatui 0.26
TrMen added code to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11729] enforce a call stack depth limit for all calls
kit494way tweaked the parser to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11717] allow comments in match blocks
kik4444 tweaked 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11705] ``query web --query``
 to return 
``list<list<string>>``
 like the scraper crate's 
``ElementRef::text()``
crides 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11702] improved colors for file-like completions
KAAtheWiseGit 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11314] fixed a panic when parsing an empty file
